"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/49983","Department of Health","false","2014-05-13","<p>Following public allegations of child euthanasia, the Department launched inquiries into them. These allegations, while serious, did not include details of specific cases, and we continue to urge those with any relevant information to contact the police in the first instance.</p>","North Norfolk","Norman Lamb","197923 ; 197924","2014-05-13T12:00:00.00Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/49983/answer","Biography information for Norman Lamb","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/49983/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/49983/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2014-05-06",,"1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, when he plans to publish full details of the circumstances which led to his Department's investigation into child euthanasia; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Sir David Amess","Southend West","Mr David Amess","197925"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/49984","Department of Health","false","2014-05-13","<p>Following public allegations of child euthanasia, the Department launched inquiries into them. These allegations, while serious, did not include details of specific cases, and we continue to urge those with any relevant information to contact the police in the first instance.</p>","North Norfolk","Norman Lamb","197924 ; 197925","2014-05-13T12:00:00.00Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/49984/answer","Biography information for Norman Lamb","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/49984/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/49984/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2014-05-06",,"1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, when his Department's investigation into child euthanasia will be concluded; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Sir David Amess","Southend West","Mr David Amess","197923"
